cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper proposes a new training loop for deep reinforcement learning agents using an evolutionary generator for procedural content generation. As such, it is likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), game theory (cs.GT), computer vision (cs.CV), and control systems (cs.SY). However, given the focus on deep reinforcement learning and evolutionary algorithms, cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely categories.
